explanation: [0-0] A little girl stands on the gray-white floor tiles at a glass door. She raises her right index finger to her mouth, gesturing "quiet." She is wearing a white sweater, black leggings, and a black floral skirt, with two white flowers in her hair. Behind her, cars are parked on the street, and rows of houses stand on the opposite side.
[0-3] The little girl walks forward, followed closely by another little girl wearing the same clothes and making the same gesture. This little girl has a white flower in her hair.

[3-13] They walk into the store, a bakery, where pastries are displayed on shelves by the door. They continue forward, revealing cakes inside a glass window display among the bread. They walk behind a man dressed in black and blue jeans, wearing a black chef's hat. The man stands with his back to them in front of a display case, arranging pastries on the shelves. The two girls raise their right hands and pat the man's back. The man feels the pats, spreads his black-gloved hands, and turns around to see. The two little girls hide behind him and follow him as he moves. While the man is not paying attention, the two little girls run through a white wooden door behind the display case. The man playfully chases after them, waving his hands.
